SABIE –  The Hawks arrested Johannes Oosthuizen (56) for the possession of an unlicensed firearm and ammunition. Oosthuizen  briefly appeared in the  Sabie Magistrate`s Court yesterday and he was released on R2 000.00 bail.  Hawks spokesman Dineo Sekgotodi said an intelligence driven operation by members of Mpumalanga (Hawks ) Serious Organised Crime Investigation Unit resulted in the arrest of Oosthuizen who was found in possession of an unlicensed firearm. ” The serial number was erased and  he was found with 64 shotgun rounds.” The matter was postponed  until June 8 for further investigation.